00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:51,690
Get ready to give the orders.

551
00:30:52,120 --> 00:30:52,520
Okay.

552
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:53,450
Don't do it too early.

553
00:30:53,610 --> 00:30:55,280
Wait for me to say, "Conflict!" before doing so.

554
00:30:55,550 --> 00:30:56,880
You must recreate Jiang Tao's response at that time.

555
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:14,180
The decelerator boards are rising. It's effective.

556
00:31:16,800 --> 00:31:17,250
No.

557
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:19,400
You were facing the panel, Captain Jiang.

558
00:31:23,770 --> 00:31:24,240
Conflict!

559
00:31:24,990 --> 00:31:26,310
Maintain the middle line and hit the brakes!

560
00:31:54,940 --> 00:31:55,490
Again.

561
00:32:28,500 --> 00:32:30,510
How much money did the company spend on the simulation?

562
00:32:30,530 --> 00:32:31,240
I'll transfer you.

563
00:32:31,870 --> 00:32:32,310
There's no need.

564
00:32:33,440 --> 00:32:34,240
The company will take care of it.

565
00:32:35,800 --> 00:32:37,250
I can't do that.

566
00:32:38,360 --> 00:32:39,560
I can't afford to pay back my life, though.

567
00:32:42,500 --> 00:32:43,520
Don't think like that.

568
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:45,820
The plane didn't catch on fire that day.

569
00:32:46,410 --> 00:32:47,410
Even if I hadn't rushed in,

570
00:32:47,650 --> 00:32:48,730
you would have been safe.

571
00:32:50,320 --> 00:32:51,030
Look.

572
00:32:52,220 --> 00:32:53,200
We did three simulations,

573
00:32:53,900 --> 00:32:55,020
and Captain Jiang was right all three times.

574
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:57,310
I was wrong again.

575
00:33:00,830 --> 00:33:01,610
Actually,

576
00:33:02,710 --> 00:33:04,320
I knew Captain Jiang's data was right

577
00:33:04,340 --> 00:33:05,750
even before we used the simulator.

578
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:07,700
Then—

579
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:09,620
I made us use the simulator only because

580
00:33:10,360 --> 00:33:12,190
I wanted you to know Captain Jiang wasn't picking on you.

581
00:33:16,830 --> 00:33:17,290
I understand now.

582
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:20,100
However,

583
00:33:20,500 --> 00:33:22,150
If I were the pilot,

584
00:33:22,800 --> 00:33:23,900
I would have chosen to steer too.

585
00:33:25,490 --> 00:33:25,970
Why?

586
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,500
During an emergency,

587
00:33:29,410 --> 00:33:30,590
braking is risky.

588
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:32,650
No matter how good a simulation is,

589
00:33:32,760 --> 00:33:34,130
it cannot perfectly model

590
00:33:34,190 --> 00:33:36,020
the force with which a pilot brakes,

591
00:33:36,040 --> 00:33:37,130
and their response time

592
00:33:37,370 --> 00:33:38,220
during an emergency.

593
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:40,200
Even 1cm

594
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:41,360
makes a difference.

595
00:33:41,780 --> 00:33:43,150
But as a pilot,

596
00:33:43,540 --> 00:33:45,490
you steered precisely, and the plane did not slip.

597
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:46,330
These are the facts.

598
00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:48,040
So,

599
00:33:48,490 --> 00:33:49,330
you agree with me?

600
00:33:50,670 --> 00:33:52,050
I agree with your choices.

601
00:33:52,630 --> 00:33:53,350
But if Captain Jiang's accusations

602
00:33:53,370 --> 00:33:54,540
were true,

603
00:33:54,660 --> 00:33:55,160
you would be in the wrong.

604
00:33:55,900 --> 00:33:56,860
Obeying the captain's orders

605
00:33:57,860 --> 00:33:59,890
is not only a rule, but also a matter of discipline.

606
00:34:00,350 --> 00:34:00,790
But—

607
00:34:00,820 --> 00:34:02,620
No buts. You must accept this.

608
00:34:06,890 --> 00:34:07,510
I accept.

609
00:34:09,560 --> 00:34:10,880
At least the aircraft's safety was ensured.

610
00:34:11,330 --> 00:34:12,340
I will accept the rest.

611
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:17,060
How will they penalize me this time?

612
00:34:17,909 --> 00:34:18,530
Ground handling?

613
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:21,790
That was a hypothetical.

614
00:34:23,750 --> 00:34:25,030
At the meeting, you claimed

615
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:27,630
you steered at the same time

616
00:34:27,770 --> 00:34:29,260
that Captain Jiang gave the orders.

617
00:34:30,590 --> 00:34:31,210
Right!

618
00:34:31,659 --> 00:34:32,350
That means

619
00:34:33,030 --> 00:34:34,429
I didn't defy his orders.

620
00:34:34,620 --> 00:34:35,920
I only acted on instinct.

621
00:34:37,630 --> 00:34:38,139
But

622
00:34:38,389 --> 00:34:39,889
I can't prove that.

623
00:34:40,639 --> 00:34:42,409
That's right,

624
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:43,210
not with the cockpit recording.

625
00:34:43,510 --> 00:34:44,219
But it's different

626
00:34:44,239 --> 00:34:45,840
with the flight data recorder.

627
00:34:45,929 --> 00:34:47,090
I have already asked Director Xie

628
00:34:47,110 --> 00:34:48,120
to consider both sets of data

629
00:34:48,120 --> 00:34:49,530
in the subsequent investigation.

630
00:34:49,810 --> 00:34:50,949
This can prove

631
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:52,170
the veracity of your claims.

632
00:34:56,110 --> 00:34:56,739
Thank you.

633
00:35:00,110 --> 00:35:02,700
I just want to uncover the facts.

634
00:35:05,600 --> 00:35:06,880
Stop denying it.

635
00:35:07,980 --> 00:35:09,130
You saved my life too.

636
00:35:10,290 --> 00:35:11,390
If this were in the olden times,

637
00:35:11,970 --> 00:35:14,160
I would have to entrust myself to you.

638
00:35:23,510 --> 00:35:25,550
I'm just joking, don't be nervous.

639
00:35:30,980 --> 00:35:32,400
You've received my gift?

640
00:35:34,750 --> 00:35:35,380
Yes.

641
00:35:36,160 --> 00:35:37,230
Don't trouble yourself in the future.

642
00:35:37,370 --> 00:35:38,250
They're quite unhealthy.

643
00:35:38,410 --> 00:35:39,380
You really ate them?

644
00:35:39,660 --> 00:35:40,110
Yes.

645
00:35:40,770 --> 00:35:41,690
I ran five extra rounds.

646
00:35:48,200 --> 00:35:48,720
Instructor Gu.

647
00:35:51,010 --> 00:35:52,980
I will become an excellent captain.

648
00:35:53,910 --> 00:35:54,630
I won't let you down.

649
00:35:58,780 --> 00:35:59,120
I'll be off now.

650
00:36:30,160 --> 00:36:30,740
Song,

651
00:36:31,030 --> 00:36:31,980
why are you here?

652
00:36:33,100 --> 00:36:34,020
I don't want to talk about it.

653
00:36:34,310 --> 00:36:35,160
We have a leak upstairs.

654
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,570
It's a flood.

655
00:36:37,330 --> 00:36:39,040
Have you informed the landlord?

656
00:36:39,270 --> 00:36:39,800
Yes.

657
00:36:40,140 --> 00:36:40,830
But it will take

658
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,680
at least a month

659
00:36:43,310 --> 00:36:44,490
to get it cleaned up.

660
00:36:45,170 --> 00:36:46,260
What will you do in the meantime?

661
00:36:47,030 --> 00:36:48,390
I can only move out.

662
00:36:48,790 --> 00:36:49,950
The landlord refunded me.

663
00:36:50,590 --> 00:36:52,290
I'll return to the hostel.

664
00:36:53,160 --> 00:36:53,470
Since

665
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:55,120
it's only temporary,

666
00:36:55,390 --> 00:36:55,860
Xiazhi,

667
00:36:56,120 --> 00:36:57,600
shouldn't we lend our extra bedroom

668
00:36:57,620 --> 00:36:59,270
to Song?

669
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:03,840
I ate too much.

670
00:37:03,860 --> 00:37:05,070
I'll drink some tea to digest it.

671
00:37:11,180 --> 00:37:11,660
Yuheng,

672
00:37:12,390 --> 00:37:13,450
I cannot impose on you.

673
00:37:13,710 --> 00:37:14,870
No it's okay.

674
00:37:15,670 --> 00:37:16,840
Xiazhi isn't angry at you.

675
00:37:19,590 --> 00:37:21,390
Why not you take a look at the room before making a decision?

676
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,680
The balcony and the kitchen are a bit small.

677
00:37:25,680 --> 00:37:26,640
I hope you don't mind.

678
00:37:26,670 --> 00:37:28,140
-It’s OK. -You can do your laundry on the balcony.

679
00:37:29,950 --> 00:37:31,340
You can exercise there.

680
00:37:32,150 --> 00:37:32,930
Let me take a look.

681
00:37:42,240 --> 00:37:42,770
Song,

682
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:44,880
this is your room.

683
00:37:47,220 --> 00:37:47,940
There used to be

684
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:49,750
three of us here.

685
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:51,980
The other girl got married and moved out.

686
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:53,910
It's comfortable here for Xiazhi and I

687
00:37:53,930 --> 00:37:55,110
so we haven't looked for another roommate.

688
00:37:56,340 --> 00:37:57,670
These boxes are ours.

689
00:37:57,700 --> 00:37:58,690
You can move them away at any time.

690
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:00,160
This bed is new.

691
00:38:00,630 --> 00:38:01,490
Let me try it.

692
00:38:05,590 --> 00:38:06,130
Yuheng.

693
00:38:06,770 --> 00:38:07,500
Even though this is only temporary,

694
00:38:07,680 --> 00:38:08,440
I will pay the rent

695
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:09,440
in full.

696
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:10,040
There's no need.

697
00:38:10,040 --> 00:38:10,480
Excuse me.

698
00:38:22,330 --> 00:38:22,820
Song,

699
00:38:25,290 --> 00:38:27,060
I have conditions if you move in with us.

700
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:29,130
First. You must do all the chores.

701
00:38:29,600 --> 00:38:31,590
Second. You collect all the deliveries.

702
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:32,840
Third—

703
00:38:32,890 --> 00:38:33,840
Other than cooking,

704
00:38:34,110 --> 00:38:35,520
I can also make stews and milk tea.

705
00:38:35,830 --> 00:38:36,450
I can make all sorts of flavors.

706
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:38,850
Third

707
00:38:39,490 --> 00:38:40,320
is also the most important.

708
00:38:41,660 --> 00:38:42,420
You're not allowed to touch my food.

709
00:38:52,180 --> 00:38:53,000
What's up with her?

710
00:39:31,510 --> 00:39:32,170
What are you doing?

711
00:39:52,290 --> 00:39:52,820
I'll get going first.

712
00:39:53,100 --> 00:39:53,410
OK.

713
00:39:59,490 --> 00:39:59,890
Yuheng,

714
00:40:02,180 --> 00:40:03,080
why are you here?

715
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:05,580
You're still suspended, right?

716
00:40:07,800 --> 00:40:08,860
When you left the house this morning,

717
00:40:08,890 --> 00:40:09,810
has Xia woken up yet?

718
00:40:14,260 --> 00:40:15,710
I was scared that she would feel awkward

719
00:40:16,270 --> 00:40:17,500
if I stayed at home.

720
00:40:18,170 --> 00:40:18,680
Right.

721
00:40:19,850 --> 00:40:21,090
She was so down yesterday.

722
00:40:22,720 --> 00:40:23,610
Perhaps

723
00:40:24,700 --> 00:40:26,060
she will feel better

724
00:40:26,390 --> 00:40:27,090
after her suspension ends.

725
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:31,340
Yuheng,

726
00:40:32,420 --> 00:40:33,270
you're so nice.

727
00:40:33,950 --> 00:40:35,060
You're always so considerate.

728
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:43,270
I have to get on a flight now.

729
00:40:44,550 --> 00:40:44,870
Bye.

730
00:40:45,020 --> 00:40:45,380
Bye.

731
00:40:59,210 --> 00:40:59,550
Got it.

732
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:02,540
Hello.

733
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:04,740
Welcome to my live stream.

734
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:07,090
I am your friend, Xia.

735
00:41:07,530 --> 00:41:10,130
Long time no see.

736
00:41:10,210 --> 00:41:11,680
Do you miss me?

737
00:41:11,980 --> 00:41:13,300
There aren't many of you here right now.

738
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:14,640
I'll sing for you first

739
00:41:14,750 --> 00:41:16,180
to warm up. Okay?

740
00:41:33,420 --> 00:41:34,780
For the simulator. Take it.

741
00:41:46,200 --> 00:41:46,870
Why are you here?

742
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:49,680
I had a meeting upstairs. I came down to see you.

743
00:41:57,850 --> 00:41:59,990
It's been very happening here the past few days.

744
00:42:04,950 --> 00:42:06,830
I've heard about the investigation meeting.

745
00:42:07,670 --> 00:42:08,350
Cheng Xiao...

746
00:42:08,380 --> 00:42:08,920
She's okay.

747
00:42:09,790 --> 00:42:11,080
I approve of her actions.

748
00:42:11,640 --> 00:42:13,240
The investigation results will also prove

749
00:42:13,430 --> 00:42:14,060
she didn't defy the captain's orders

750
00:42:14,080 --> 00:42:15,260
on purpose.

751
00:42:22,270 --> 00:42:23,310
Have you seen the netizens' comments?

752
00:42:25,960 --> 00:42:26,550
What comments?

753
00:42:31,610 --> 00:42:32,530
Someone got hold of the

754
00:42:32,550 --> 00:42:33,880
land-air communications

755
00:42:34,420 --> 00:42:35,130
and posted it on the Internet.

756
00:42:37,700 --> 00:42:39,270
Some aviation bloggers believe that

757
00:42:39,830 --> 00:42:41,860
the female pilot had acted without permission,

758
00:42:42,260 --> 00:42:43,230
causing a passenger to get injured.

759
00:42:45,580 --> 00:42:46,940
I'm afraid that if the matter blows up,

760
00:42:47,600 --> 00:42:48,390
it'd be bad for Cheng Xiao.
